daily active users. Cloudflare, our reverse proxy, uses a unique session cookie for anti-DDOS measures.</p><h2>HTTPS</h2><p>The website and websocket connections are served over secure sockets.</p><h2>Tracking<span class="slash">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span>External analytics</h2><p>Airmash does not use any external analytics suites such as Google Analytics. We do not embed externally hosted social media buttons.</p><p class="padtop">The above privacy policy is subject to change at any time without prior notice.</p><p class="grey padtop">Last updated on December 3rd, 2017</p></div><div class="footer">Copyright &copy;2017 Airmash. All rights reserved.</div></div></body></html>